sloth
-----
A stupid HTTP tarpit.

USAGE
    sloth -host {host} -port {port} -wait {N}

ARGUMENTS
    flag    description         defaults
    ----    -----------         --------
    -host   host                localhost
    -port   port                8080
    -wait   wait interval (ms)  8000

BUILD
    Run `make' to generate the binary in `./bin'/
